<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SpotIt DB Management</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .card {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-sync {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }

        .btn-sync:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }

        .btn-force {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #000;
        }

        .btn-force:hover {
            background-color: #e0a800;
        }

        .btn-drop {
            background-color: #dc3545;
        }

        .btn-drop:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }

        .alert-danger {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        }

        code {
            background: #eee;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>üõ†Ô∏è Database Management Panel</h1>

    <% if (message) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-success">
            <%= message %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

            <% if (error) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-danger">
                    <%= error %>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Database Operations</h3>
                        <p>Use these tools to manage the database schema. <br><strong>Note:</strong> "Force Sync" and
                            "Drop" are destructive actions.</p>

                        <form action="/db-panel" method="POST" class="actions">
                            <button type="submit" name="action" value="sync" class="btn btn-sync">Sync DB
                                (Alter)</button>
                            <button type="submit" name="action" value="force_sync" class="btn btn-force"
                                onclick="return confirm('WARNING: This will DELETE ALL DATA and recreate tables. Are you sure?')">Force
                                Sync</button>
                            <button type="submit" name="action" value="drop" class="btn btn-drop"
                                onclick="return confirm('CRITICAL WARNING: This will DELETE THE ENTIRE DATABASE SCHEMA. Are you sure?')">Drop
                                DB</button>
                            <button type="submit" name="action" value="seed_admin" class="btn btn-sync"
                                style="background-color: #17a2b8;">Seed Admin</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Legend</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Sync (Alter)</strong>: Updates schema to match models (Safe-ish). Adds columns,
                                etc.</li>
                            <li><strong>Force Sync</strong>: <code>DROP TABLE IF EXISTS</code> then
                                <code>CREATE TABLE</code>. Deletes data.</li>
                            <li><strong>Drop DB</strong>: Drops all tables. Database becomes empty.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
</body>

</html>